original_title: Chikara Tag World Grand Prix 2008 - Night 2
overview: November 9th, 2008 :: The second night of the Tag World Grand Prix features the final two rounds of the tournament! Plus, in a "Best of 3 Falls" match, Mike Quackenbush faces longtime rival Claudio Castagnoli! Other matches featured include: • F.I.S.T.  & Emil Sitoci vs Marc Roudin, Joel Redman & Wade Fitzgerald • 2.0 & Karsten Beck vs Kid Fite, Lionheart & Sha Samuels • Big Van Walter vs Bad Bones.
title: Chikara Tag World Grand Prix 2008 - Night 2
